{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"white","bgm":"stop","narrationBg":"","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.0},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"[textBlack:\"...SAFE!\"]"},{"narration":"[textBlack:WooOOOOOOOO!!]"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":305251,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303901,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeOutTime":1.0},{"bgm":"bgm03_story09","chara":[{"id":305251,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Ashley","textBg":"shout","textLeft":"Whoooah! Two points in one go!","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303901,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Seira","textBg":"shout","textRight":"A comeback walkout! Woohoo!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":305251},{"effect":"fadeout","id":303901}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301650,"motion":100,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"[chara:301650:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]We did it! We won!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":301650}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":302950,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Those were great runs, you two."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"That was some fine decision-making. Avoiding@overtime at all costs was the right call."},{"chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Though I still think your run was a bit on the@rash side, Miss Kagami,"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"but then again, they wouldn't have tripped up otherwise."},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":302950,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Masara","textLeft":"I remembered your words, Coach."},{"chara":[{"id":302950}],"nameLeft":"Masara","textLeft":"That we wouldn't have stood a chance against@them head-on,"},{"chara":[{"id":302950}],"nameLeft":"Masara","textLeft":"so we needed to overtake them at a decisive@moment."},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"id":302950,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301650,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kokoro","textLeft":"Huh… So you actually thought about it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301650}],"nameLeft":"Kokoro","textLeft":"For a second, it felt to me like you got swept up@by the excitement, too."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":302950,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Masara","textRight":"I would never…"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":301650}],"narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":302950,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"But then, Masara paused for a moment…@and corrected herself."},{"chara":[{"id":302950,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Masara","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"…I'm not sure, actually. I might've lost some@of my composure at the time."},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":302950}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":800101,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800301,"motion":0,"pos":2}]},{"chara":[{"id":800101}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Congrats. As much as it pains us to admit,@you crushed us back there."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":800301}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"But we'll get you back next year, just you wait!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800301}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301650,"motion":400,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"[chara:301650:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Thinking about next year already? Geez…"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":301650}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":305251,"motion":200,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303901,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Ashley","textLeft":"[chara:305251:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]Picture perfect!@Now that's what a good stream's made of!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20331.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationBg":"bg_adv_20331.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"So we won the tournament, and as promised,@the coach listened to the team's plea.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story05","chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameCenter":"","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"I'll keep my promise."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801000}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"You wanted me to play for Japan in the World@Cup again…was it?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"id":801000,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Yeah, we did… But we've all thought about it@some more since then…"},{"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"During our long days of practice,@all of us: me, Masara, and the juniors, we could@feel just how much the coach liked baseball…@How much she liked sports in general.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20331.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_14053.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"autoTurnLast":2.4,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20331.jpg","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20331.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"And so…we decided to ask@for something a little different.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"You want me to keep playing baseball@for my own sake…?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":801000}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800100,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Yeah…!"},{"chara":[{"id":800300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"We could tell how serious you were when you@drew up our strategies today."},{"chara":[{"id":800300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"And you looked like you were having such a good@time when the crowds gathered up to watch…"},{"chara":[{"id":800300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"So we thought it'd be better if you went back@to the ballpark not for us or anything else,"},{"chara":[{"id":800300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"but instead for yourself."},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800100},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800300}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20331.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"autoTurnLast":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800102,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800200,"motion":0,"pos":2}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800102},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800200}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20331.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"autoTurnLast":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800201,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800302,"motion":0,"pos":2}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800201},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800302}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"You girls…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801000}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"…You're right, I might've been too stuck on@making it to the Olympics."},{"chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"I think I forgot how much I simply enjoyed@the sport…"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"id":801000,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Does that mean…?!"},{"chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"But making a comeback isn't as easy as you@think. I'd need to find a team to join first…"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"nameCenter":"???'s Voice","textCenter":"Hello."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":800300},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801000}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800300},{"effect":"fadeout","id":801000}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20331.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"autoTurnLast":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800600,"motion":0,"pos":1}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"id":800600,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301650,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kokoro","textLeft":"Oh…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":302950,"motion":100,"pos":2},{"id":301650,"mouthOpen":0}],"nameRight":"Masara","textRight":"You're the other team's coach, I believe?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800600,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Yeah. Just stopping by to say hello and speak@with your coach about something."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"With me…?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":800600}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Remember who I am?"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Er… [chara:801000:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:801000:lipSynch_1][chara:801000:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Ahhh!@I can't believe I never noticed!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301650,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kokoro","textLeft":"Wait… You know each other?"},{"bgm":"bgm24_story08","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"It turns out, the other team's coach@was actually in the same high school@baseball club as ours back in the day!","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20331.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"Apparently she's working@in sports PR right now…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800600}],"narration":"And the next thing we knew,@she said something really surprising:"},{"chara":[{"id":800600}],"nameRight":"","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"…You see, a pro baseball team is looking@into making a women's roster,"},{"chara":[{"id":800600}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"and the scout in charge of it asked me@to introduce you to them."},{"chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Huh…?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301650,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kokoro","textLeft":"Oh, wow…!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800600,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I'd say I have a decent understanding@of your situation."},{"chara":[{"id":800600}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"…But, why obsess over the Olympics still?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800600}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"There are plenty of other international@tournaments you could play in."},{"chara":[{"id":800600}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"And I'm sure your late father would've told@you the same thing."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801000}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Yeah…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800600}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Plus, as long as you stay in the game,"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":800600,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"you might even see the IOC change up their rules@and finally introduce Women's Baseball someday!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800100,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Oh, don't worry about us!"},{"chara":[{"id":800300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"We'll work extra hard, and we'll win next year@on our own!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801000,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":801000}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"…Thanks, all of you."},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800100},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800600,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"So, you said a scout wanted to meet me…@Can you tell me more?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_24012.jpg","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeInTime":1.3},{"autoTurnLast":3.0,"turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.5},{"autoTurnLast":3.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21111.jpg","narrationBg":"","narrationCoverOpacity":160.0,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.2},{"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"A few things happened after that…","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.0},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":305251,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationBg":"","narrationCoverOpacity":160.0,"narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":305251,"motion":200}],"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"From what I hear, Ash's stream unexpectedly@took off on the internet, and people rushed@to join the team we helped with.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21421.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationBg":"","narrationCoverOpacity":160.0,"narrationEffect":"in"},{"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"So I guess their future is looking up.@Although, Masara's Swimming Club junior seems@to be having trouble balancing the team@and club at the same time.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21111.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":300201,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301601,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationBg":"bg_adv_21111.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"And as for our coach…","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":300201,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Natsuki","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"[chara:300201:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]…Look at this baseball magazine article!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301601,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kokoro","textLeft":"Wow, it's our coach on there!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":300201,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Natsuki","textRight":"Yeah, can you believe how big the news of her unretiring got?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":302901,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Masara","textLeft":"Good for her."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":300201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Natsuki","textRight":"Y'know, this is getting me all pumped up! Maybe@I should get on with some hard work of my own…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301601,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kokoro","textLeft":"Huh? Are you going back to baseball@too, Natsuki?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":300201,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Natsuki","textRight":"Ahaha, nah, for cheerleading!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":300201,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Natsuki","textRight":"See, this whole thing's really touched me."},{"chara":[{"id":300201}],"nameRight":"Natsuki","textRight":"Like, it's such a good reminder of how someone's@passion can inspire others and spur them to act."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":300201,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Natsuki","textRight":"And I'd say that applies to cheerleading@just as well!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":301601,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kokoro","textLeft":"\"Someone's passion spurring someone else\"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"autoTurnLast":0.7,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"effect":"slideInLeftFast","face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":302950,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"…!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"chara":[{"effect":"slideOutRightFast","id":302950}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21111.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301601,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":302901,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Kokoro","textLeft":"…Mhm, yeah. I'd say you're absolutely right!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":302901,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Masara","textRight":"…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":302901,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Masara","textRight":"Why are you staring at me while saying that?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
